  "Description": {
    "English": "Gathers resources directly from the interstellar medium, via a complex system of suction intakes and condensing tubes. The gathered substance <span class=\"name name-technology\">varies</span> with the local <span class=\"name name-technology\">star classification</span>.<br><br>Powered directly from the freighter's main electrical loop. Functionality is entirely <span class=\"name name-stellar\">autonomous</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用复杂的吸气口和冷凝管系统直接从星际介质中收集资源。收集的物质随当地<span class=\"name name-technology\">星体分类</span>而具有<span class=\"name name-technology\">不同种类</span>。<br><br>直接由货船的主电力回路提供动力。功能完全<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自主</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "透過複雜的吸取和冷凝管系統，直接從星體中心收集資源。收集而來的資源會因當地的<span class=\"name name-technology\">星球分類</span>而<span class=\"name name-technology\">有所不同</span>。<br><br>直接透過貨船的主電子迴圈充電。功能完全<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自動</span>。"
  },
